      "- Formal review of documents and credit",
      "- Verifies your income, debts, and creditworthiness",
      "- Rate typically locked for 90-120 days",
      "- Carries more weight with sellers",
      "",
      "**Bottom line**: Always get pre-approval before making offers.",
      "",
      "## Documents You'll Need",
      "",
      "Lenders typically require:",
      "",
      "**Income Verification**:",
      "- Last 2 pay stubs",
      "- T4 slips from past 2 years",
      "- Letter of employment",
      "- Notice of Assessment (NOA) from CRA",
      "",
      "**Self-Employed**:",
      "- Tax returns (T1 General) for 2 years",
      "- Business financial statements",
      "- NOAs confirming no taxes owed",
      "",
      "**Assets**:",
      "- Bank statements (3 months)",
      "- Investment account statements",
      "- RRSP/TFSA statements if using for down payment",
      "",
      "**Down Payment Verification**:",
      "- Bank statements showing funds sitting for 90+ days",
      "- Gift letter if receiving family help",
      "- Proof of RRSP withdrawal (HBP)",
      "",
      "## The Pre-Approval Process",
      "",
      "**Step 1**: Gather your documents",
      "**Step 2**: Apply online, by phone, or in-branch",
      "**Step 3**: Lender verifies your information (1-3 days)",
      "**Step 4**: Receive pre-approval letter with rate and amount",
      "**Step 5**: House hunt with confidence",
      "",
      "**Timeline**: Typically 1-3 business days",
      "",
      "## How Much Can You Afford?",
      "",
      "Lenders use two key ratios:",
      "",
      "**Gross Debt Service (GDS)**: Housing costs ≤ 32% of gross income",
      "- Mortgage payment",
      "- Property taxes",
      "- Heating",
      "- 50% of condo fees",
      "",
      "**Total Debt Service (TDS)**: Total debt ≤ 40% of gross income",
      "- Everything in GDS",
      "- Plus car loans, credit cards, student loans",
      "",
      "**Example**: $80,000 annual income",
      "- Maximum GDS: $2,133/month",
      "- Maximum TDS: $2,667/month",
      "",
      "## Pre-Approval Limitations",
      "",
      "Pre-approval is conditional and depends on:",
