      "",
      "## The Break-Even Calculation",
      "",
      "**Formula**: Penalty + Costs ÷ Monthly Savings = Months to break even",
      "",
      "**Example**: $8,000 penalty + $1,500 costs ÷ $250 monthly savings = 38 months to break even.",
      "",
